                     <interp inst="t18330103-50-person551" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I have a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction (read) - I know him to be the person who was convicted in the July Session; I was present at his trial.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I am innocent.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18330103-50-verdict299" type="verdictDescription">
